# Testing & Quality Assurance

## Automated Tests

- Run Python tests: `pytest tests/`
- Run TypeScript tests: `npm test` in `/ui`
- Smart contract testing: `truffle test` or `hardhat test`

## Coverage & CI/CD

- Code must pass automated CI on every PR.
- Aim for >80% test coverage in critical business logic.

## Manual QA
- Use provided test scenarios for end-to-end review.
- Document usability and regression tests in this file or `/tests`.

See workflow in `.github/workflows/ci.yml`.